stabber
------------------------------------------
Stabber acts as a stubbed XMPP service for testing purposes.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libexpat1-2.8.0-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.88.2-1
  libmicrohttpd12-1.0.2-1bl1
  libstabber-devel-0.1.0+git20260306-1bl1
  libstabber0-0.1.0+git20260306-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  libexpat-devel-2.8.0-1
  libglib2.0-devel-2.88.2-1
  libmicrohttpd-devel-1.0.2-1bl1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/profanity-im/stabber

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/profanity-im/stabber.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack stabber-0.1.0+git20260306-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./stabber-0.1.0+git20260306-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/stabber-0.1.0+git20260306-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/stabber-0.1.0+git20260306-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libstabber0-0.1.0+git20260306-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libstabber-devel-0.1.0+git20260306-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(stabber)
  /usr/bin/stabber.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/stabber.README
  /usr/share/doc/stabber/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/stabber/README.md

(libstabber0)
  /usr/bin/cygstabber-0.dll

(libstabber-devel)
  /usr/include/stabber.h
  /usr/lib/libstabber.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/stabber.pc

